jphase

Interface DiscPhaseVar

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JMarkovElement, PhaseVar
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDiscPhaseVar, DenseDiscPhaseVar, SparseDiscPhaseVar

    public interface DiscPhaseVar
extends PhaseVar
    This interface defines the behaviour that any Discrete Phase-Type distribution should have
    Author:
    Juan F. Perez, German Riano. Universidad de los Andes. (C) 2006
